Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志们 和寒冷战斗到底啊 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个混蛋说今年是暖冬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿三倍衣服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是雪啊 雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再吹风了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高...高见女子高中的同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们应该是坐前一列特快来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 苍荣的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻装上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全副武装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么天寒地冻的你们这是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天3夜的冬季合宿 in 长白鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 所以画好正确的装备寄给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:55.34,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山猫座炭：不穿得暖暖的是不行的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身都是光的咧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首先要面对的就是这寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那细微的缝隙里一点一点传来的寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有克服了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能在这冷天里进行活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是星见妹妹和小矢 准备得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君和江户川君穿得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样也是好好准备了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身牛仔裤穿了和没穿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的冬天装备是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化纤织料这类能够吸汗速干的衣料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绒布或是毛衣这类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以留住空气的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不透风的材料最好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作裤之类的 能很好的留住体温
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有帽子发热片等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在适当地加上各种各样的附加装备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好带了点能加的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也把短衬裤穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也带了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是以为白天会热而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了 其他事情再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次请多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气 毕竟要4天3夜在同吃同住的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜一下子就歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你不是新部长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有在高天联见过了的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地打招呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们也很紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就心跳如小鹿一般...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生相片 让我照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气转晴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里天气很多变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杉野市的今年还没开始下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见到这么厚的雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都去过那么多地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到哪都觉得什么都很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸还在的时候虽然经常带我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在了以后就不怎么出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要说对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么 恋爱关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一般学校里不是到处都是情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的世界观有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们办事疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连合宿的地方都没定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是 能一起来我们很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣的同学们是第一次来冬季合宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为天文部是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过冬季的星座都已经很熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户座和昴星团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季大三角和冬季大六角形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然见过但也只是在城市里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 绝对会让你们更感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 星见妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好期待啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得猎户座是美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是大胡子猎人大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想要美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样打扮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里反而应该是大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你萌胡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文台圆顶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到室内呼出的气还是白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖气供应有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都这样的 过会儿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿我们要自己做饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 先去看看自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把行李给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很重的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人拿的动的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生宿舍在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面装了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等会见 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有发热片也拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双脚已经没感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止都没这样玩过雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好换上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 居然能和女高中生有那么多的身体接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我可要往死里的照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三波同学 秋菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是来帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样的话会被雪烧伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这次要做什么观测？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往年都是年初的时候来合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测四分仪座流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年因为月光的原因只好改了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以主要是观察和摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们来说是最后一次合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能尽兴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不放晴的话也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来合宿就把这个因素考虑进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自己选的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直喊好冷好冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找些能一起穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身裤和作睡衣的运动裤都穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿不上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来只是想要在雪景里穿得可爱点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的时候在车上看到了好像是便利店的店子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有内衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 不要让手脚发冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 要随身携带好自己的手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三 出门前要告诉别人自己去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好有亲和力高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来播报各地天气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上空有强冷空气 受其影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长白鹤地区可能突降大雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长白鹤地区？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店不哪里都是24小时营业的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且美星说看到她到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都黑了 为什么她要一个人出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没听我们说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 她那时就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没听到啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 在我们修暖气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大雪里 那个不习惯风雪天气的孩子独自在外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静下来 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在旅馆里再找一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她确实带够了备用的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你看到她时的情形详细地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白茫茫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挖个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家那里就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 要镇定 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要顺着自己的脚印就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的脚印...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西南北都分不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能走远了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本看不清前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古今中外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 到我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么窗子开着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是睡觉的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说啊 我白天可是很努力的干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那一望无际的雪铲啊铲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了设营的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能让我玩一下啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星大概也追出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经联系了消防队了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的暴风雪下不知什么时候能来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那两人能找到一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在播放各地的天气情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长白鹤地区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能是为了摄影取景到后面的森林去了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把范围定在公交站的那个方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去找丢了的东西的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回到了镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常还是会发生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是摄影点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再前面就是雪地和森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野也不好 很容易迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冻成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家多担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方离别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还那么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要多打扮自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使不出力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天谴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 电钻头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来叫声「电钻头」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么电钻头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电钻头 电钻头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是天生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这下 恐怕真的糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么漂亮的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:15:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点紧张感都没有的白痴卡通是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOT！ 小熊发热片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 我怎么会有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大龄...美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你一个人出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不见你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你是不是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身是什么装备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 运动服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回到大家那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 完全看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在车站的话恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我们一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会胡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬姬 美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是先把手电筒给我了 会发生什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后还是不知道方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 天晴了就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意！ 现在还在下大雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正好有个能避雪的洞 太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}把美星拖出来留下的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我以前也一个人在下大雪时跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后挨骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为穿过大雪就能看到星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然非常冷 心里也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风雪后的星星果然好美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 偷跑出来也要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在云的上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么轻快...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在高处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人在下面嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊那里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你关心我 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说学姐是云的话 我就是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越积越厚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道现在不是说这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是学姐 请再正视我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果学姐不把我当作对手的话 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于大八木君的感情我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风停了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕宿五 参宿七 五车二 北河三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参宿四 南河三 天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星太多了 都连不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光箭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果迷失了方向 要见到这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 乱来也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了有事尽管跟我们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服的话想要多少都借你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太担心 小夜都瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们平安无事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 终于能暖暖身子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏要开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点神志不清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来比谁能在室外看到更多星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能找到更好的观星地点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手 对手 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.51,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社 最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:49.30,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空的环
